📘 SOC Analyst Security Playbook

A short, actionable playbook for daily SOC operations.

1. Alert Triage Workflow

• Validate alert source
• Check context (user, host, time)
• Pull logs from SIEM/EDR
• Identify TTPs
• Map to ATT&CK
• Escalate or close with justification


2. Incident Response Flow

• Identify
• Contain
• Collect evidence
• Analyze
• Remediate
• Recover
• Document
• Lessons learned


3. IOC Handling

• Enrich (VT, HA, Shodan)
• Classify (benign, suspicious, malicious)
• Add to blocklists or watchlists
• Update detection rules


4. Threat Hunting Cycle

• Hypothesis
• Data collection
• Analysis
• Findings
• ATT&CK mapping
• Recommendations


5. Daily SOC Checklist

• Review SIEM dashboards
• Check EDR alerts
• Monitor identity logs
• Validate critical patches
• Review firewall/VPN logs
• Update threat intel feeds


